&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Own&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive net-new pipeline by designing and executing field marketing programs: webinars, trade shows, in-person events, and digital activations, ensuring a focus on ROI from the start&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build multi-touchpoint, integrated campaigns that move leads through the funnel using ads, email, social, content, and more, optimizing ruthlessly based on performance data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with sales to align marketing activity directly to pipeline goals; communicate clearly on metrics that matter to leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage AI tools to accelerate campaign development, personalize outreach, analyze performance, and find competitive edges faster&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and evaluate third-party and co-marketing demand generation opportunities with a sharp eye on cost-per-opportunity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work cross-functionally with Product Marketing to develop and repurpose content that converts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support customer marketing programs that protect and expand existing relationships through cross-sell and retention initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor pipeline health and make real-time adjustments to keep numbers on track or ahead of plan&lt;/li&gt;
