&lt;p&gt;Our team is changing the face of legal, immigration, compliance, and operational risk. Today, our products run over 20,000+ corporations of all sizes across the globe, representing a large portion of the Fortune 10, almost 40 percent of the Fortune 500, and over 50,000 users in over 150 countries. These teams depend on our technology and our people to help them grow and protect their organizations. Our approach to work is proactive, collaborative, and committed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an excellent opportunity to join our growing company by supporting our most valued asset – our customers. In this role, you will gain an in-depth understanding of our customer’s operations, goals, and challenges so that you can help them gain the most value from their investments with Mitratech.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
