&lt;p&gt;Mitratech&#39;s CaseCloud is a Salesforce-native legal operations platform on the AppExchange. This role is dedicated to building and shipping Agentforce agents and AI components for CaseCloud — packaged for commercial distribution through the Salesforce AgentExchange. You will work directly with product management to translate agent blueprints into production configurations, and with the development team to ensure every AI component meets AppExchange quality and security standards.&lt;/p&gt;
